Jelix Installation
==================

Server configuration
---------------------

Jelix works with PHP 5.6 and higher, but PHP 7.3+ is prefered

This php extensions should be installed : xml, simplexml, pcre, session, spl, json, mbstring et tokenizer.

Jelix supports these databases: MySQL 5.5+, PostgreSQL 9.0+, SQLite 3.

installation
------------

- unzip the archive
- create an application with the bin/create-jelix-app script
- set write access on temp/ and var/* directories, for the web server

Details
-------

see https://docs.jelix.org/fr/manuel-1.7/mise-en-route
or https://docs.jelix.org/en/manual-1.7/getting-started
